{"tid":1368854,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"2019夏 - 日文班 / 韓文班","createTime":"2019-07-26T14:43:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T07:58:11.000Z","uid":2771,"like":19,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"a12dcd9d41f699ccd60d2c50c478327fc9a0a43a","tid":1368854,"uid":2771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:43:54.000Z","msg":"大家好！我哋又準備開日文班啦！<br />\n上次大家都好踴躍，開咗Google form好快就有好多人填咗<br />\n雖然唔能夠比所有人都參與到、亦回唔到本，但開心嘅係，留到最後嘅同學仔都好俾心機，仲叫我地快啲開進階班<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以喺嚟緊八月開始，我哋將會同步有入門班同埋進階班，等唔同進度嘅朋友仔可以揀番啱自己嘅課堂<br />\n時間方面都會照舊係平日放工後/週末，方便大家<br />\n地點方面都照舊喺旺角租課室，可能需要大家夾返少少租場錢，但求打個和<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有興趣嘅巴打絲打就快啲填Google form啦！<br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/6GNy2L2ZDrsz9gmh9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2F6GNy2L2ZDrsz9gmh9&d=0Lcuuml91xlF79uKCzc07kngG4XMVyvHznkFIzn%2BcUY%3D&h=163123de\" target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/6GNy2L2ZDrsz9gmh9</a><br />\n<br />\n另外，我哋今次會有位朋友加入黎教韓文，<br />\n佢學習韓文超過6年，已經考咗Topik level 5<br />\n亦曾經教過小組興趣班、上門補習，<br />\n有興趣學韓文嘅巴打絲打可以填下面嘅Google form，老師會就返大家嘅程度同興趣開班 ;)<br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/YQ8zwEHitfPF8TfA8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FYQ8zwEHitfPF8TfA8&d=0Lcuuml91xlF79uKCzc07kngG4XMVyvHznkFIzn%2BcUY%3D&h=113c26d2\" target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/YQ8zwEHitfPF8TfA8</a>"},{"pid":"afd27d8767dae518649917c6145005b45c8b381d","tid":1368854,"uid":2771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:46:34.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"bc771507a30c53aec423c7ede09f9ca09870979d","tid":1368854,"uid":2771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:46:46.000Z","msg":"721記得出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e36769410d16a594d0f42fdfe026740afca25fc8","tid":1368854,"uid":2771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bc771507a30c53aec423c7ede