plyTime":"2019-08-08T11:13:36.000Z","msg":"想問下最basic既日文班開左未，仲有冇位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T04:26:14.000Z","msg":"下星期六仲可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T08:23:15.000Z","msg":"填左表呀 無回音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dfc7f673f4bde40238029e7f80c0d68421cb4df","tid":1368854,"uid":72253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a12dcd9d41f699ccd60d2c50c478327fc9a0a43a","tid":1368854,"uid":2771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:43:54.000Z","msg":"大家好！我哋又準備開日文班啦！<br />\n上次大家都好踴躍，開咗Google form好快就有好多人填咗<br />\n雖然唔能夠比所有人都參與到、亦回唔到本，但開心嘅係，留到最後嘅同學仔都好俾心機，仲叫我地快啲開進階班<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以喺嚟緊八月開始，我哋將會同步有入門班同埋進階班，等唔同進度嘅朋友仔可以揀番啱自己嘅課堂<br />\n時間方面都會照舊係平日放工後/週末，方便大家<br />\n地點方面都照舊喺旺角租課室，可能需要大家夾返少少租場錢，但求打個和<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有興趣嘅巴打絲打就快啲填Google form啦！<br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/6GNy2L2ZDrsz9gmh9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2F6GNy2L2ZDrsz9gmh9&d=0Lcuuml91xlF79uKCzc07kngG4XMVyvHznkFIzn%2BcUY%3D&h=163123de\" target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/6GNy2L2ZDrsz9gmh9</a><br />\n<br />\n另外，我哋今次會有位朋友加入黎教韓文，<br />\n佢學習韓文超過6年，已經考咗Topik level 5<br />\n亦曾經教過小組興趣班、上門補習，<br />\n有興趣學韓文嘅巴打絲打可以填下面嘅Google form，老師會就返大家嘅程度同興趣開班 ;)<br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/YQ8zwEHitfPF8TfA8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FYQ8zwEHitfPF8TfA8&d=0Lcuuml91xlF79uKCzc07kngG4XMVyvHznkFIzn%2BcUY%3D&h=113c26d2\" target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/YQ8zwEHitfPF8TfA8</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T17:46:08.000Z","msg":"想問旺角教室方唔方便輪椅？"},{"pid":"4a0b8926425b443e319f87b1c3b0d768a67c359a","tid":1368854,"uid":2771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5dfc7f673f4bde40238029e7f80c0d68421cb4df","tid":1368854,